high_descs: Turn and go to the right to face the white table.
Pick the white bowl up from the table.
Go back to the left and turn again to stand in front of the counter with the lettuce on it.
Put the bowl on the counter.
Pick the fork up from the counter.
Put the fork in the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put a fork in a bowl on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the right end of the white table.
Pick up the glass bowl that is on the white table.
Turn left and walk over to the section of counter to the right of the toaster.
Put the glass bowl on the counter to the right of the head of lettuce.
Pick up the metal fork that is just below the head of lettuce on the counter.
Put the fork inside the glass bowl handle down.
anns.task_desc: Put a metal fork into a glass bowl on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the door then turn left.
Pick up the glass bowl on the white table.
Turn left, walk towards the refrigerator, hang a left, walk towards the counter.
Place the glass bowl in between the fork and knife.
Pick up the fork on the left side of the bowl
Place the fork inside the bowl
anns.task_desc: Place the glass bowl on the counter top

high_descs: Move to the table to the left of the door
Pick up a bowl from the table
Move to the counter to the right of the toaster
Place the bowl on the counter
Pick up a fork from the counter
Place the fork inside the bowl on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a fork inside on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room, then hang a left and walk to the white table
Pick up the clear bowl that is sitting on the table to the right of the soap bottle
Turn left and cross the room, turn left at the fridge and walk to the counter across the room
Place the bowl on the counter
Below and to the right of the lettuce,
Pick up the fork that is sitting on the counter and place it in the clear bowl
anns.task_desc: Place a fork in a bowl

high_descs: Turn around and head to the table on the right.
Pick up the bowl from the table.
Turn left and go to the sink, turn left again to the counter.
Set the bowl on the counter.
Pick up the fork from the counter.
Put the fork in the bowl on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Take a bowl and fork over to the counter.
